Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.73,0:00:09.98,PZ,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\shad1\fn萝莉体\bord3\an8\c&H82CFEB&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(470.4,398.4)\4c&H000000&}但如果從這裡出去 獲得自由
